Band Contest - Darlington The Order of Druids Annual Brass Band Contest and Gala was held in the beautiful grounds at Woodlands. The bands entered were Linthwaite, near Huddersfield; Northallerton Temperance; Whitworth, near Spennymoor; Darlington Operatic; The Malleable Ironworks, Stockton; and New Shildon Sax.Horn.
